Package: cnvtools2
Type: Package
Title: Functions for analyzing DNAcopy formatted CNV data with limma
Version: 1.0
Date: 2013-04-24
Author: Giovanni d'Ario
Maintainer: Giovanni d'Ario <giovanni.dario@isb-sib.ch>
Description: The package DNAcopy produces segmented data in a format that can
    be easily exported in a data frame. This package splits the segments such
    that each patient, for each chromosome, will have the same number of
    segments. This allows the creation of rectangular matrices that can be
    analyzed with limma.
License: GPL-2
Collate:
